data.title: The Princess Srinagarindra Award - Marhesya Syani
data.meta_description: The Princess Srinagarindra Award - Marhesya Syani.docx - Free download as Word Doc (.doc / .docx), PDF File (.pdf), Text File (.txt) or read online for free. The document contains a nomination form for the Princess Srinagarindra Award submitted on behalf of Marhesya Syani by the Ministry of Health of the Republic of Indonesia. It includes biographical information about Marhesya Syani, a nurse working at a public health center in South Jakarta. The nomination cites Marhesya's innovation of a "TEENS HEALTH CARE" program to improve adolescent health services through youth-friendly initiatives at her facility. Additional signatures are required to certify the nomination.
